text: Liu Reng-sun (born 28 October 1941) is a Taiwanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Taiwan Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
